headline: Defense Contractors Stocks Q3 Teardown: ICF (NASDAQ:ICFI) Vs The Rest
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at ICF (NASDAQ:ICFI) and the best and worst performers in the defense contractors industry.
